        // Code completion
        Eclipse.completion("System.out.println");
        // Code refactoring
        Eclipse.refactor("System.out.println");
    }
}
```

#### Visual Studio Code

* Extensive library of extensions for various programming languages
```scss
// JavaScript code
console.log("Hello, World!");
```

#### Sublime Text

* Customizable keyboard shortcuts and syntax highlighting
```scss
